{"word":"G3036 - λιθοβολέω - lithoboléō - lith-ob-ol-eh'-o - Stone","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">λιθοβολέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">lithoboléō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">lith-ob-ol-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Stone</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கல்லெறி"},{"paragraph":"to stone"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G3037 - λίθος - líthos - lee'-thos/3037\">G3037</a> and <a href=\"#/G906 - βάλλω - bállō - bal'-lo/906\">G906</a>; to <i>throw stones</i>, that is, <i>lapidate:</i> - stone, cast stones.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2642/2642\">G2642</a>, <a href=\"#/G3034/3034\">G3034</a>, <a href=\"#/G3036/3036\">G3036</a>"}]}